data.description: Picture yourself living in this beautiful and bright two-story home located in the heart of Bushkill. This home is move-in ready and offers 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. The heart of this home is the large and open living room that includes a stunning fireplace to keep you warm. The open floor plan, high ceilings, and large porch offer the perfect home for gatherings or relaxation. A partially finished basement is the cherry on top for this home. This premier community is well-known for its amenities including indoor and outdoor pools, indoor tennis, a ski slope, a hot tub, and a restaurant/bar
